def entrance(n):
    fib_sequence = [1, 1]
    while len(fib_sequence) <= n:
        new_value = (fib_sequence[-1] + fib_sequence[-2]) % 1000
        new_value = new_value if new_value != 0 else 1000
        fib_sequence.append(new_value)
    return fib_sequence[n - 1]
